fr:mainmatter.html:p: We provide a brief description of the Jason-DTU system, including the overall system design and the tools that we used in the Multi-Agent Programming Contest. We also provide a detailed evaluation of our system. The strengths of our system include dynamic assignment of agents to groups, enabling flexible use of agents according to the current situation. Our team performed overall very well and we won some matches by either a fairly big margin or closely.
